==Chinese==

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī shí èr niǎo

===Etymology===
Literally: one stone, two birds.

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[石]][[二]][[鸟]]'''

# [[kill two birds with one stone]]; do one task and finish two or more goals.

===Alternate forms===
[[一石二鳥]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

===Related terms===
*[[一箭双雕]]
*[[一举两得]]
*[[一石二鳥]] ([[Japanese]])
*[[一挙両得]] ([[Japanese]])

